history.content:
It appears that anyone trying to override a conflict with CS70 has not succeeded. Has anyone who filled out the manual override form for CS70 succeeded in getting the class? If not, there's going to be a big problem because phase 2 is ending soon and we will lose our seats.

Also, if phase 2 does happen to roll around and they still haven't resolved our issue, are those who had this problem going to get any chance of keeping their seats? 

Edit: it seems that most people are getting conflicts from the midterm times and that they are working on removing the midterm from the class listing. Maybe that's the issue, because I actually have a conflict with another class (EE105 discussion) and the form wasn't getting processed, possibly due to the midterm conflicting with another class's midterm
